{Godena,M (2485)-Van den Doel,E (2547) Mondariz 2000 1-0 (78)}) 8. Bb3 $146 (8.
Bg5 h6 9. Bxf6 Qxf6 10. Nd5 Bxd5 11. Bxd5 Rab8 (11... Kh8) 12. c3 Ne7 13. Bb3
Bb6 14. Nh2 Kh8 15. Kh1 Qh4 16. Nf3 Qf6 17. Nh2 Qh4 18. Nf3 Qf6 19. Nh2 Qh4 {
1/2-1/2 (19) Boros,D (2338)-Halasz,T (2359) Hungary 2011}) 8... Bxb3 9. axb3 h6
{Controls g5} 10. Be3 Bxe3 11. fxe3 a6 {Covers b5} 12. Ne2 d5 13. exd5 Nxd5 14.
Qd2 Nf6 15. e4 Kh7 16. Ng3 g6 {Secures f5+h5} 17. Rad1 Qe7 18. Qc3 Rad8 19.
Rfe1 Qb4 20. Qxb4 Nxb4 21. Rd2 Rfe8 22. Rf1 Kg7 {Black king safety dropped} 23.
Rdf2 Nd7 24. d4 (24. Nh4 $5 {deserves consideration} f6 25. Ra1 $11) 24... exd4
$17 25. Nxd4 Ne5 26. Nf3 Nbc6 (26... Rd7 27. Rc1 $17) 27. Ne2 $15 Nxf3+ 28.
Rxf3 Ne5 {A valuable piece} 29. R3f2 Rd2 30. Nc3 Red8 31. Nd5 Rxf2 32. Rxf2 ({
Inferior is} 32. Kxf2 c6 33. Ne3 Rd4 $17) 32... c6 {Black threatens to win
material: c6xd5} 33. Nc3 b5 34. b4 $2 (34. Kf1 $142 $11 {would keep White alive
}) 34... Rd4 $17 35. Ne2 $2 (35. Na2 $142 $5 $17) 35... Rxb4 $19 36. Nf4 (36.
b3 $19) 36... Rxb2 37. Kh2 (37. c3 {what else?} Rb1+ 38. Rf1 $19) 37... a5 38.
Rd2 (38. Rf1 {does not improve anything} Rxc2 39. Ra1 g5 40. Nh5+ Kg6 $19)
38... a4 (38... a4 39. Ne2 a3 $19) 0-1

