Rd4 Bc6 $15) 28... Rec8 (28... Reb8 29. h5 $19) 29. Be2 (29. b3 Ra3 $17) 29...
Bc6 30. Bd1 Bb5 (30... Ba4 31. b3 Bxb3 32. Bxb3 cxb3 33. Rxb4 Rxa2 34. Rb1 $19)
31. f5 (31. b3 Rcb8 $17) 31... Rd8 (31... Rc5 32. Bg4 exf5 33. Bxf5 $19) 32.
Bg4 (32. g4 $142 $5 $17) 32... exf5 $19 33. Bxf5 Bd7 34. Bxe4 (34. Bxd7 Rxd7
35. f3 exf3 $19) 34... dxe4 35. Rxc4 Rdb8 (35... b3 {makes it even easier for
Black} 36. a3 Rac8 37. Rxe4 $19) 36. Rd1 $2 (36. Rxe4 $142 $5 Be6 37. f3 $17)
36... Bf5 $19 37. Rdd4 (37. Rc7+ Kg8 38. Ra1 Rb5 $19) 37... Rxa2 38. Rxb4 (38.
g4 {cannot change what is in store for White} Bxg4 39. Rxe4 Bf5 40. e6+ Kf6 $19
) 38... Rxb2 39. Rxb8 Rxb8 40. g4 Bxg4 41. Rxe4 Bf5 42. Ra4 Rb7 43. Kg2 Kg6 44.
Kg3 (44. Ra6+ {does not save the day} Kh5 45. Kg3 Bc8 $19) 44... Kh5 (44... Be6
