40. Qxd8+ Kf7 41. Qaf6#) 34... Kg7 35. Rd7+ Kh6 36. Qc3 Kg5 (36... a5 {is not
the saving move} 37. Qg7+ Kg5 38. Qxf8 Kg4 39. c8=Q Re1+ 40. Kg2 Rg1+ 41. Kxg1
Kh5 42. Qc1 a4 43. Rxh7+ Kg4 44. Qf4#) 37. h4+ Kg4 (37... Rxh4 {doesn't change
